===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# Hard to grasp; not [[obvious]] or easily [[understood]]; barely noticeable. This happens when people don't notice things.
#: ''The difference is '''subtle''', but you can hear it if you listen carefully.''
# [[insidious]]
# (of a thing) cleverly [[contrived]]; (of a person) [[skillful]]
# [[cunning]]

